msgid "# LoRA Adapters Guide"
msgstr "# LoRA适配器指南"

msgid "## Overview"
msgstr "## 概述"

msgid ""
"Like vLLM, vllm-ascend supports LoRA as well. The usage and more details can"
" be found in [vLLM official "
"document](https://docs.vllm.ai/en/latest/features/lora/)."
msgstr ""
"与vLLM一样，vllm-"
"ascend也支持LoRA。具体用法和更多细节可参考[vLLM官方文档](https://docs.vllm.ai/en/latest/features/lora/)。"

msgid ""
"You can refer to [Supported "
"Models](https://docs.vllm.ai/en/latest/models/supported_models/) to find "
"which models support LoRA in vLLM."
msgstr ""
"您可以查阅[支持的模型](https://docs.vllm.ai/en/latest/models/supported_models/)了解vLLM中哪些模型支持LoRA。"

msgid ""
"You can run LoRA with ACLGraph mode now. Please refer to [Graph Mode "
"Guide](./graph_mode.md) for a better LoRA performance."
msgstr "您现在可以使用ACLGraph模式运行LoRA。请参考[图模式指南](./graph_mode.md)以获得更好的LoRA性能。"

msgid "Address for downloading models:"
msgstr "模型下载地址："

msgid ""
"- base model: <https://www.modelscope.cn/models/vllm-ascend/Llama-2-7b-hf/files>\n"
"- lora model: <https://www.modelscope.cn/models/vllm-ascend/llama-2-7b-sql-lora-test/files>"
msgstr ""
"- 基础模型：<https://www.modelscope.cn/models/vllm-ascend/Llama-2-7b-hf/files>\n"
"- LoRA模型：<https://www.modelscope.cn/models/vllm-ascend/llama-2-7b-sql-lora-test/files>"

msgid "## Example"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid ""
"We provide a simple LoRA example here, which enables the ACLGraph mode by "
"default."
msgstr "这里我们提供一个简单的LoRA示例，默认启用ACLGraph模式。"

msgid "## Note"
msgstr "## 注意"

msgid ""
"- We have implemented LoRA-related AscendC operators, such as bgmv_shrink, "
"bgmv_expand, sgmv_shrink and sgmv_expand. You can find them under the "
"\"csrc/kernels\" directory of [vllm-ascend repo](https://github.com/vllm-"
"project/vllm-ascend/tree/main/csrc/kernels)."
msgstr ""
"- "
"我们已实现了与LoRA相关的AscendC算子，例如bgmv_shrink、bgmv_expand、sgmv_shrink和sgmv_expand。你可以在[vllm-"
"ascend仓库](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/tree/main/csrc/kernels)的\"csrc/kernels\"目录下找到它们。"

msgid ""
"- You can enable LoRA with dense or mixture-of-experts(MoE) models now ([PR "
"#10977](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/10977)). However, "
"we haven't support expert-parallel(EP) or quantification yet when you run "
"MoE models with LoRA."
msgstr ""
"- 你现在可以在稠密模型或混合专家（MoE）模型上启用LoRA（[PR #10977](https://github.com/vllm-"
"project/vllm-ascend/pull/10977)）。不过，在使用LoRA运行MoE模型时，我们尚未支持专家并行（EP）或量化功能。"
